        public void setCenter(GeoPoint center)
        Set the center of this request
        Parameters:
        center - The center of the region in which to get data. Northern latitudes are positive and southern latitudes are negative. Eastern hemisphere longitudes are positive and western hemisphere longitudes are negative. Longitudes in North America are negative. The latitude and longitude values are expressed using the WGS 84 datum.

        public void setRadius(double radius)
        Set the radius of this request
        Parameters:
        radius - The radius of the circular bounding area from which to return data. Any features that are fully or partially enclosed within the bounding area are selected. If the Units parameter is set to Metric, the radius is measured in meters; if Units is set to MILES, the radius is measured in miles.
